tool_description: An API for calculating the compatibility of two people for a love relationship using astrology, horoscopes and synastry.
name: Astro Matcher API
title: Astro Matcher API

api_list.name: Score
api_list.description: Returns only the overall match score for the relationship.

required_parameters.name: a
required_parameters.description:
Object with the birthday (including time in UTC) and location of the 1st person.
The following properties are required: year, month and day.
The following properties are recommended: hour, minute, latitude and longitude.

required_parameters.name: b
required_parameters.description:
Object with the birthday (including time in UTC) and location of the 2nd person.
The following properties are required: year, month and day.
The following properties are recommended: hour, minute, latitude and longitude.

api_list.name: Match
api_list.description: Returns the two horoscopes, the synastry and our rating of the relationship.
